translation.Name: Belgium Note - Nulirane Research Facility #4
translation.Interactability_Text_Line_0: I hope the right person sees this letter. But I’m Dr. Tykenov and I’m trapped here in the Nulirane Research Facility in Belgium. No one is permitted to leave, except for certain personnel. The work conducted here I cannot take part of no more.
translation.Interactability_Text_Line_1: All of us are being monitored and the doors are sealed quite shut. Please get me out of here!
